{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-single-post-js","path":"/sidebar-olusturma","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"c2cd45c4-e607-5e5c-8fc5-1f7fe0e3c5b3","html":"<p>Bu yazımda ürün kategorilerinden oluşan sidebarı halledeceğiz. Sol üst köşede sidebarın açılacağı hamburger ikonumuz olacak. Tıkladığımızda bize kategorileri gösterecek. Sidebarın sağ köşesinde kapatmak için buton olacak. İlk olarak hamburger butonu ile başlayalım. </p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"0\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;brand&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">                </span><span class=\"mtk4\">&amp;#9776;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;index.html&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;trendol&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">div</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Brand altına button ekliyoruz. İçine hamburger butonu oluşturacak kodu yazıyoruz. kodu çalıştırdığımızda stil verilmemiş bir hamburger görürüz.</p>\n<div><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 331px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/b0dc8b400aa7ab0da11db9c5d9712f3b/62452/hamburger.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 41%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"hamburger\" title=\"hamburger\" src=\"/static/b0dc8b400aa7ab0da11db9c5d9712f3b/62452/hamburger.png\" srcset=\"/static/b0dc8b400aa7ab0da11db9c5d9712f3b/772e8/hamburger.png 200w,\n/static/b0dc8b400aa7ab0da11db9c5d9712f3b/62452/hamburger.png 331w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 331px) 100vw, 331px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></div>\n<p>   Şimdi ihtiyacımız olan şey bu butona stil vermek.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"1\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.brand</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">font-size</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">3</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">font-weight</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">900</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">padding</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">.5</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">background</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">none</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">border</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">none</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">cursor</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">pointer</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">outline</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">none</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Hamburgerin büyük görünmesi için font-size ve font-weight ile ayarlama yapıyoruz. İstenmeyen çizgiden kurtulmak için border ve outlineı none veriyoruz. Sadece bordera none vermek yetmiyor, eğer outline ayarlamazsak üzerine tıkladığımızda da istemediğimiz bir çerçeve ile karşılaşıyoruz. Son olarak cursor ise buton üzerine geldiğimizde oku el ikonuna çeviriyor. </p>\n<div><span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 240px; \">\n      <a class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\" href=\"/static/863660531e2f3c4e721a61923b8ec6ee/8ff5a/hamburger1.png\" style=\"display: block\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 72%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/png;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n  <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" alt=\"hamburger\" title=\"hamburger\" src=\"/static/863660531e2f3c4e721a61923b8ec6ee/8ff5a/hamburger1.png\" srcset=\"/static/863660531e2f3c4e721a61923b8ec6ee/772e8/hamburger1.png 200w,\n/static/863660531e2f3c4e721a61923b8ec6ee/8ff5a/hamburger1.png 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 240px) 100vw, 240px\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\" loading=\"lazy\">\n  </a>\n    </span></div>\n<p> Hamburgerin verdiğimiz stilden sonraki hali bu.\nGelelim sidebar için oluşturacağımız eventi yazmaya. Önce sidebar oluşturup click event oluşturalım.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"2\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">aside</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;sidebar&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">h3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Kategoriler&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">h3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">                &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;index.html&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Kazak&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;  </span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">                &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">href</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;index.html&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Pantolon&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">a</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">            &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">li</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">ul</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">aside</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Header taginden hemen sonra ve main taginden önce konumlandırıyoruz. Şu durumda kodumuzu çalıştırırsak en altta kategoriler kısmını görebiliriz. Şimdi sayfamızda konumlandırma işlemini yapalım.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"3\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.sidebar</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">position</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">fixed</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">  </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">transition</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">all</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk4\">.3</span><span class=\"mtk7\">s</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">transform</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">translateX</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk4\">-30</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">width</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">30</span><span class=\"mtk7\">rem</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">background-color</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">white</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">height</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk4\">100</span><span class=\"mtk7\">%</span><span class=\"mtk1\">;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.sidebar.open</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">transform</span><span class=\"mtk1\">: </span><span class=\"mtk9\">translateX</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk4\">0</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">}</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Buradaki ilk sınıfta 30remlik bir genişlik verdik. Bu genişliği tamamen saklamak içinse translateX -30rem veriyoruz. Böylece sidebarımız tamamen sol tarafta gizlenmiş olacak. İkinci sınıfımız ise iki sınıfa (sidebar, open) aynı anda dahil olduğunda devreye girecek. TranslateX e 0rem verdiğimiz için sidebar tamamen görünecek. “Transition” ise sidebar görünüp kaybolurken kayma efekti verecek. Tabi ki bu sınıflar tek başına tüm işi halledemez. Şimdi JS fonksiyonlarını yazalım. Biraz önce eklediğimiz hamburger butonu içine onclick eventini ekliyoruz.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"4\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">     &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">onclick</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk5\">openMenu</span><span class=\"mtk6\">()&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">       </span><span class=\"mtk4\">&amp;#9776;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">     &lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Sırada bu fonksiyonu yazmak var. En alta body tagi üzerine bir script tagi açıyoruz. İçine fonkiyonlarımızı tanımlayacağız.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"5\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">script</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    function openMenu()</span><span class=\"mtk7\">{</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        document.</span><span class=\"mtk5\">querySelector</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;.sidebar&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">).classList.</span><span class=\"mtk5\">add</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk7\">}</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">script</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>İlk fonksiyonumuzu oluşturduk. Artık hamburger butonuna bastığımızda sidebar açılacak. Şimdilik kapatma özelliğimiz yok. Sıradaki işimiz ise onu oluşturmak.\nSidebar içinde kategoriler yazısı altına bir buton oluşturuyoruz ve içine yine onclick  eventi ekliyoruz. </p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"html\" data-index=\"6\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">h3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;Kategoriler&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">h3</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        &lt;</span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">class</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;sidebar-close-button&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">onclick</span><span class=\"mtk1\">=</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk5\">closeMenu</span><span class=\"mtk6\">()&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;X&lt;/</span><span class=\"mtk7\">button</span><span class=\"mtk1\">&gt;</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Ve script tagi içine bu fonksiyonumuzu da tanımlayalım.</p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"js\" data-index=\"7\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"mtk9 mtki\">function</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> </span><span class=\"mtk5\">closeMenu</span><span class=\"mtk1\">() {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">        document.</span><span class=\"mtk5\">querySelector</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;.sidebar&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">).classList.</span><span class=\"mtk5\">remove</span><span class=\"mtk1\">(</span><span class=\"mtk6\">&quot;open&quot;</span><span class=\"mtk1\">);</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    }</span></span></span></code></pre>\n<p>Bu fonksiyon butona basıldığında geçerli olan open sınıfını kaldırır. Kodu çalıştırırsak artık X butonuna bastığımızda sidebarı kapatabildiğimizi görürüz. Şimdi kapama butonuna stil verelim. </p>\n<pre class=\"grvsc-container monokai\" data-language=\"css\" data-index=\"8\"><code class=\"grvsc-code\"><span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk5\">.sidebar-close-button</span><span class=\"mtk1\"> {</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"grvsc-line\"><span class=\"grvsc-source\"><span class=\"mtk1\">    </span><span class=\"